#: ../../source/scanning_paper_drawings.rst:54
msgid "Restart the computer."
msgstr "Reiniciar el sistema."

#: ../../source/scanning_paper_drawings.rst:56
msgid "**Macintosh only - To remove the scanner TWAIN drivers:**"
